This paper deals with the quality of metadata in a biomedical repository, which involves issues related to data management, information retrieval, and data curation. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.DL (Digital Libraries), followed by cs.DB (Databases), cs.IR (Information Retrieval), cs.CY (Computational Biology and Bioinformatics), and cs.CR (Cryptography and Security).
